Description: Self-contained replication package for "Public support for global
    vaccine sharing in the COVID-19 pandemic: Evidence from Germany"
    (PLOS ONE, 2022; doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0278337). Provides analysis
    data, preparation scripts, table and figure builders, precomputed report
    artifacts, and tests.
